All kinds of scripts:

 opp_makemake - create makefile for a simulation
 splitvec     - split an output vector file to separate vectors
 splitvec.bat - splitvec's DOS version
 dos2unix     - convert text files to Unix
 seedtool.cc  - generates seeds for random number generators
 readme       - this file
 tcl2.c       - utility for embedding Tcl source into an executable
 prephtml     - used during development
 replace.c    - MSVC: substitute @something@ variables into makefiles, .bat files

--VA
